The paper discusses the integration of SDN and VANET, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also focuses on security threats and countermeasures, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the development of intelligent transportation systems and IoT-enabled advertising, which falls under the category of information technology (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the benefits and challenges of SDVN architectures, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the future directions of research, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
